  <p>Dear Maria,</p>
  <p>Thanks for your letter. I &#xA0;<input id="q1" type="droptarget"/>&#xA0; your family is okay and &#xA0;<input id="q2" type="droptarget"/>&#xA0; affected too badly &#xA0;<input id="q3" type="droptarget"/>&#xA0; the awful floods last week.</p>
  
  <p>In your letter you ask for advice about ways of raising money for the disaster and I've &#xA0;<input id="q4" type="droptarget"/>&#xA0; up with a few ideas. I &#xA0;<input id="q5" type="droptarget"/>&#xA0; advise you to ask for donations because people might be suspicious that the money won't get to &#xA0;<input id="q6" type="droptarget"/>&#xA0; victims. It's also not very easy to ask people for money like this.</p>
  
  <p>If I &#xA0;<input id="q7" type="droptarget"/>&#xA0; you, I'd try to organize &#xA0;<input id="q8" type="droptarget"/>&#xA0; sponsored walk or run. I'm sure you could get lots of students from your university involved. You don't &#xA0;<input id="q9" type="droptarget"/>&#xA0; to do too much for this. You &#xA0;<input id="q10" type="droptarget"/>&#xA0; just make sure people have enough time to get as many sponsors as possible before the event. If you want to do something in addition to &#xA0;<input id="q11" type="droptarget"/>, I'd &#xA0;<input id="q12" type="droptarget"/>&#xA0; you to hold a bring-and-buy sale. All you need to do is book a hall and get as many of &#xA0;<input id="q13" type="droptarget"/>&#xA0; friends involved as you can.</p>
  
  <p>However, I &#xA0;<input id="q14" type="droptarget"/>&#xA0; you should be aware that people can sometimes be unreliable and not turn up to events or not give you &#xA0;<input id="q15" type="droptarget"/>&#xA0; money they promised, so you'd &#xA0;<input id="q16" type="droptarget"/>&#xA0; not start working out how much you've raised until they've actually given &#xA0;<input id="q17" type="droptarget"/>&#xA0; to you.</p>
  
  <p>Anyway, I &#xA0;<input id="q18" type="droptarget"/>&#xA0; you the very best of luck and don't &#xA0;<input id="q19" type="droptarget"/>&#xA0; to get in touch if you'd &#xA0;<input id="q20" type="droptarget"/>&#xA0; me to help in any way. I love walking!</p>
  <p>With love, </p>
  <p>Melissa</p>
